A hands-on Spring Boot project demonstrating integration with OpenAI using the Spring AI framework. Built to explore AI-powered application development with enterprise Java patterns — chat completion, prompt templating, and streaming responses.

📌 Features

✅ Chat Completion — Conversational AI using OpenAI GPT models via Spring AI's ChatClient
✅ Prompt Templates — Dynamic prompt construction using PromptTemplate
✅ Streaming Responses — Real-time token streaming with StreamingChatClient
✅ REST API Layer — Spring Boot REST endpoints to expose AI capabilities
✅ Configuration Management — Externalized API keys and model settings via application.properties


🏗️ Architecture
Client (HTTP)
     │
     ▼
Spring Boot REST Controller
     │
     ▼
Spring AI ChatClient
     │
     ▼
OpenAI API (GPT-4 / GPT-3.5-turbo)

🛠️ Tech Stack
